Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp23.maze

Class Tile

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp23.maze.Tile
Direct Known Subclasses:
ComputerChip, Exit, ExitLock, Floor, Hint, Key, LockedDoor, Wall
public abstract class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
This class is responsible for the tiles in chap's challenge. Each tile is differentiated by its own sub class.
